Formats for Date and DateTime Values in Web Data Connectors

Web data connectors can work with Date and DateTime values that use the following formats. For information about the symbols used in these format examples, see Formatting Dates and Times on the ICU User Guide site.

dd-MM-yyyy
dd-MMM
dd-MMM-yy
dd-MMM-yyyy
dd-MMM-yyyy HH:mm:ss
dd/MM/yyyy
h:mm a
HH.mm
hh.mm a
HH.mm.ss
hh.mm.ss a
hh:mm a
HH:mm:ss
hh:mma
M/d/yyyy HH:mm:ss
MM-dd-yyyy
MM-dd-yyyy HH:mm
MM/dd/yy
MM/dd/yy HH:mm:ss
MM/dd/yyyy
MM/dd/yyyy
MM/dd/yyyy HH:mm:ss
MM/dd/yyyy hh:mm:ss a
MMM yyyy
MMM-yy
MMMM dd yyyy
MMMM dd yyyy hh:mma
MMMM dd, yyyy
MMMM dd, yyyy HH:mm:ss
MMMM dd,yyyy
MMMM dd,yyyy HH:mm:ss
yyyy-MM-dd
yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm
yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss
yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS
yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS
yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS
yyyy/MM/dd
yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss
